ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A class to suffer through. No would not recommend. Reasons stated above
It's great for getting you thinking about the hard questions about your dissertation. I'd recommend it for anyone that needs to develop a research question and plan.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: In general this course did little to deepen my knowledge of the discipline. The exercise in critiquing a study was somewhat helpful as wascritiquing other students proposals.
It directly contributed to my dissertation because I had to present on my dissertation question and tentative research plan. It helped me think about and develop my research question.
